 * Conceive file mapping schema (#21)
 * Directory Listing (#22 #23)
 * Mount Notification (#26)
 * Unmounting logic (#44)

 * MIME detection (#49)

Bugs fixed:

 * All zero return value (#38)
 * Date was falsely shown as 1st Jan 1970 (#47)
 * Crash when browsing Sub-Dir (#61)
